{"arkId":"cl010113702","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113702","modified ":"2026-02-06","title":"Tabati\u00e8re","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Tabati\u00e8re"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : \u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime (Occident)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1700 - 1800","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 614 - Galerie Louis XV, Vitrine 15","room":"Salle 614, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1700,"endYear":1800,"imprecision":"","text":"XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Baudesson, Daniel","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Attribu\u00e9 \u00e0","dates":[{"date":"1716","place":"Berlin","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1785","place":"Berlin","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q50338700"},{"label":"Chodowiecki, Daniel Nikolaus","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1726","place":"Dantzig","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1801","place":"Berlin","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Emailleur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q696720"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7657","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Tabati\u00e8re d\u0027or de forme rectangulaire aux faces grav\u00e9es en mosa\u00efque d\u0027un quadrillage r\u00e9gulier. Chaque face est \u00e9maill\u00e9e en plein d\u0027un sujet mythologique peint. On peut notamment voir sur le couvercle Mars, V\u00e9nus et l\u0027Amour dans les forges de Vulcain. En bas \u00e0 droite on trouve la signature \u0022Chodowiecki\u0022. Au dessous de la bo\u00eete, une femme assise au pied d\u0027un arbre et parlant \u00e0 un jeune chasseur. Sur la b\u00e2te, diff\u00e9rents personnages mythologiques (V\u00e9nus, L\u00e9da, Diane ...).\r\nMalgr\u00e9 des d\u00e9formations, on reconnait la signature de l\u0027orf\u00e8vre berlinois Daniel Baudesson, accompagn\u00e9 dans son ouvrage du miniaturiste Daniel Chodowiecki. \r\nCette tabati\u00e8re ressemble fortement \u00e0 la OA 6752, qui a \u00e9t\u00e9 produite par les m\u00eames orf\u00e8vre et \u00e9mailleur en Allemagne, malgr\u00e9 l\u0027absence de poin\u00e7on pour l\u0027attester.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; marques illisibles (dans le fond de la bo\u00eete)\r ; Poin\u00e7on de ma\u00eetre orf\u00e8vre (dans le fond de la bo\u00eete)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"4,1","displayDimension":"4,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"8,4","displayDimension":"8,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"6,2","displayDimension":"6,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or (\u00e9maill\u00e9)\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"Allemagne (Europe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection du baron Salomon de Rothschild (1835-1864) ; collection de la baronne Ad\u00e8le de Rothschild (1843-1922) ; legs en 1922","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Rothschild, Baronne Salomon de, n\u00e9e Ad\u00e8le de Rothschild","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"},{"value":"Rothschild, Salomon de","note":"","role":